      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Please don&#39;t use this anti-pattern, it&#39;s <a href=\"http://errorprone.info/bugpattern/DoubleBraceInitialization\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">actively dangerous</a> and there are reasonable alternatives."
