      "post_id" : 8261124,
      "comment_id" : 97952589,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Another problem with this solution is that it can lead to memory leaks. Since it creates anonymoys class with reference to the instance of the owning object, leak can occur when anonymous inner class is returned and held by other objects."
