    "body" : "<p>Java has no map literal, so there's no nice way to do exactly what you're asking.</p>\n\n<p>If you need that type of syntax, consider some Groovy, which is Java-compatible and lets you do:</p>\n\n<pre><code>def map = [name:\"Gromit\", likes:\"cheese\", id:1234]\n</code></pre>\n"
