    "body" : "<pre><code>    boolean x;\n    for (x = false, \n        map.put(\"One\", new Integer(1)), \n        map.put(\"Two\", new Integer(2)),      \n        map.put(\"Three\", new Integer(3)); x;);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Ignoring the declaration of <code>x</code> (which is necessary to avoid an \"unreachable statement\" diagnostic), technically it's only one statement.</p>\n"
