      "body" : "@vikramvi yes If you look at the <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/13/docs/api/java.base/java/util/Map.html#of(K,V,K,V,K,V,K,V,K,V,K,V,K,V,K,V,K,V,K,V)\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">documentation</a> <code>Map.of</code> is only done up to 10 entries since it is quite laborious"
