    "question_id" : 8261075,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>We can use JSON to achieve this, like following using Gson</p>\n<pre><code>Map&lt;String,Integer&gt; hashMap = new Gson().fromJson(&quot;{'one':1,'two':2,'three':3}&quot;,HashMap.class);\n</code></pre>\n<p>Or using Jackson</p>\n<pre><code>Map&lt;String,Integer&gt; hashMap = new ObjectMapper().readValue(&quot;{'one':1,'two':2,'three':3}&quot;,HashMap.class);\n</code></pre>\n"
  } ],
